						<summary>

						<p>Prakāra Sēṉaimudaliyar Shrine, North wall. </p>						

						<p>1571 A.D.</p>						

						<p>This is dated in the cyclic year Prajāpati, Śravaṇa ba. 12, Thursday which may be equated to A.D. 1571 August 16, f.d.t. 39. The Śaka year is not given.</p>						

						<p>States that Padumarasa, son of Bukkarasa-paṇḍita, visited (and worshipped) god Raṅganātha.</p>						

